data.description: Experience Elegance and Flexibility in this 4-Bedroom (or 3+ Flex Room), 2-Bath Home in Sebastian Cove. Built in 2019, this St. Augustine gem offers a versatile floor plan to suit your needs. A spacious, open kitchen with granite countertops is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the Florida weather on the covered lanai, and take advantage of Sebastian Cove's community amenities. Modern, move-in ready, and waiting for you to make it home. Don't miss out - schedule a viewing today!
